## File Structure & Code Organization

### Core Components (src/components/)
- **`MapPage.tsx`** (823 lines): Main UI orchestration, all modals, search, GPS, proposal flow
- **`Map.tsx`** (272 lines): Leaflet integration, pin rendering, popup HTML with submitter names

