### Data Layer (src/lib/, src/types/)
- **`locationStore.ts`** (147 lines): Frontend cache, D1 interface, Location mapping
- **`geopoint.ts`** (78 lines): TypeScript interfaces for all data structures
- **`webhookUtils.ts`**: HMAC signature verification utilities

### Configuration
- **`schema.sql`** (22 lines): D1 database schema with submitter fields
- **`wrangler.jsonc`** (93 lines): Cloudflare config, domain routing, D1/secrets bindings
- **`src/sanity/schemaTypes/geopoint.ts`** (144 lines): Sanity schema with workflow fields

